
# ── Secrets — NEVER COMMIT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Centralised secrets reference lives at /root/.flirexa-secrets/SECRETS.md
# (outside any repo). This block also blocks any in-repo accidents.
SECRETS.md
SECRETS
secrets/
.secrets/
.flirexa-secrets/
*.secret
*.token
.token
*_token
*.pat
*credentials*
.credentials
.npmrc
.netrc
# Private keys and signed material
*.pem
*.key
*.key.priv
id_rsa
id_ed25519
id_*.priv
# Dotfile env (already in some repos, ensuring uniform coverage)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.production
